<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Fledged" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Fledged,</orth> already covered with feathers: <cit><quote>Shylock knew the bird was f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 3.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 1, 32</bibl></cit>. Used, in jest, of a beard: <cit><quote>whose chin is not yet f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 23</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>